title: 2 Pistols - Death Before Dishonor [2008] [Album]
description:
Death Before Dishonor is the debut album by rapper 2 Pistols, released on June 17, 2008. Guests include T-Pain, Tay Dizm, Ray J, Slick Pulla, Blood Raw, Sarah Rohman, Corey Harrison, Trey Songz, Sarah Cadle, BMU & Tyra B. A version of "Candy Coated Diamonds" featuring Fergie (instead of Tyra B) leaked on various Black Eyed Peas fansites.

Label................: Universal Republic
Genre................: Hip-Hop
StoreDate............: Jun-17-2008
